= 0.9.0

 New Features:
 * Base#find_or_initialize method (completed)
 * Add railtie for loading variables from a YAML file
 * Document hash should have sub-select functionality
 * Mongomatic#Cursor should support inject and other enumerable functions
 * Capistrano/Deployment recipe that calls create_index

 Refactor:
 * Mongomatic::Base should be a module instead of inheritence

 Deprecate:
 * Validation DSL is very verbose
